one_reviews_text: Good Concept, but 2.5 cm (random) snap is just nonsense, not to talk about the the nothing-changed updates.

This have to be the best programming team available in VR. To the intuitive Interaface, to the sensitivity of the controls, there is no other creative VR experience like this. Just when you think you want a feature, the DEV TEAM most likely has it updated by the next time you put your headset on. Has changed my 20yr experience in 3D design to the next level.
no other like this app! and they update it evry few days! super stable, amazing features! wonderful!
Glad they finally added  a File Managerwith local access, vastly more useful!. A few import formats would be handy too.
